    <!-- Main Content for About Us -->
    <main class="about-container">
        <section class="about-header">
            <h1>About Sparkle Shine Carwash</h1>
            <p>Exceptional service, attention to detail, and unmatched customer satisfaction.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-info">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 1980, Sparkle Shine Carwash has been a trusted name in the automotive care industry for over four decades. With a focus on exceptional service, we have perfected the art of car detailing and washing. Our team of skilled professionals uses state-of-the-art equipment to provide thorough, high-quality cleaning.</p>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Sparkle Shine, we specialize in both interior and exterior treatments to ensure every vehicle receives the best care. We continue to set the standard for excellence in car care, providing a comprehensive range of services to maintain the cleanliness and appearance of your vehicle. Our mission is simple: to make every car shine and exceed your expectations.</p>

            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction</strong> - We aim to provide exceptional experiences and high-quality service with every vehicle we work on.</li>
                <li><strong>Attention to Detail</strong> - Every inch of your car matters to us. We ensure no corner is left uncleaned or overlooked.</li>
                <li><strong>Expert Team</strong> - With over 50 employees, our dedicated team provides professional service with a focus on precision.</li>
                <li><strong>Environmental Responsibility</strong> - We use eco-friendly products and efficient water management practices to ensure sustainability.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="team-section">
            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team-members">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <!-- <img src="/img/team1.jpg" alt="John Doe"> -->
                    <h3>John Doe</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                    <p>With over 40 years of experience in the automotive care industry, John has led Sparkle Shine to become a trusted name in car detailing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <!-- <img src="/img/team2.jpg" alt="Jane Smith"> -->
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <p>Operations Manager</p>
                    <p>Jane is responsible for overseeing day-to-day operations, ensuring everything runs smoothly and efficiently.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <!-- <img src="/img/team3.jpg" alt="Robert Johnson"> -->
                    <h3>Robert Johnson</h3>
                    <p>Lead Technician</p>
                    <p>Robert brings his expertise in car detailing, ensuring that every service is performed with precision and excellence.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-section">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <div class="services">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="/img/intr.jpeg" alt="Interior Cleaning">
                    <a href="/"><h3>Interior Cleaning</h3></a>
                    <p>We provide thorough interior cleaning services, from vacuuming to deep upholstery treatments, ensuring a spotless and fresh cabin.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="/img/extr.jpg" alt="Exterior Cleaning">
                    <a href="/"><h3>Exterior Cleaning</h3></a>
                    <p>Our exterior cleaning services include washing, waxing, and polishing, leaving your car's exterior gleaming and protected.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <img src="/img/fullcl.jpg" alt="Full Detailing">
                    <a href="/"><h3>Full Detailing</h3></a>
                    <p>Our full detailing service covers both interior and exterior, restoring your car to like-new condition.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

